## Release Notes

- Add CODEOWNERS and settings.yml for jtox. @iphydf (#15)
- [ImgBot] Optimize images @imgbot (#12)
- Use maven pom.xml and pure java for jtox. @iphydf (#11)
- Enable .travis.yml check and use non-markdown license. @iphydf (#10)
- Add a bazel test that ensures all our projects are GPL-3.0. @iphydf (#9)
- Relicense under GPLv3. @iphydf (#8)
- Remove tox4j stuff from readme. @iphydf (#7)
- Add dependencies on native code jars. @iphydf (#6)
- Remove old scala client. @iphydf (#4)
- Add a screenshot of the application. @iphydf (#3)
- Add a simple chat tab where friend messages arrive. @iphydf (#2)
- Add a JavaFX example client in pure Java. @iphydf (#1)
